13   Eisero apa Sedekia apaashare olaiguanani Nebukadnesa, laa ninye apa oishoo ninye meinosa olmumai tialo Enkai; negolong'u ninye neitagol oltau lenye, neany eibelekenyakino Olaitoriani Enkai e Israel. 
14  Ore ilapolosak pooki kituaak, oltung'ana sii neponari aaku ilemeisiligayu, nesuj olminong le lelo oshon; neisarkionie enkaji o Laitoriani, apa naitisinya ninye te Yerusalem.


15  Ore Olaitoriani Enkai oo loo menye, neirriwaki ninche ilkiliku aimunye isinkan lenyena, enkaraki naing'urrie ninye iltung'ana lenyena, o tenkaraki emanyisho enye. 
16  Kake etigirate ninche aamor lelo sinkan le Nkai, nemenaa irorei lenyena, nesurdaay iloibonok le Nkai, o metaba anaa nedumunye engoro o Laitoriani too iltung'ana lenyena, ometaba anaa neaku meetae olmairo.


17   Ore enkaraki ina neyau aitaar ninche olaiguanani loo Lkaldayo ilo apa otasesekuana ilbarnot lenye metuata tiatua enkaji e Nkai, nemeetayie olng'ur olbarnoti anaa esila, anaa oltung'ani kitok aashu oltung'ani moruo. Neishooyo ninche apik atua enkaina enye. 
18  Ore nena masaa pooki e nkaji e Nkai nkutiti o sapuki, o lchumat pooki le nkaji o Laitoriani o lchumat lo laiguanani o lkituaak lenyena, neyai nena pooki Babilon. 
19  Nepejoo ninche enkaji e Nkai neuroo esuntai e Yerusalem, nepejoo nkajijik enyena pooki e nkitoo te nkima. Neinyal nena tokitin pooki e tipat. 
20  Eewa ninye eyararoto meshomo Babilon lelo apa ooilanya olalem, neaku isinkan lenyena, o metaba anaa neitasheyieki enkitoria e Parsia. 
21   Pee eitabari ororei lo Laitoriani oimua enkutuk e Yeremia, o metaba anaa neshipakino enkop sabato. Ore te nena olong'i pooki naitomijoonoki, neibung sabato neitabaya ilarin ntomoni naapishana.

